# ZIP layout note

These profile bundles use a flatter layout for easier browsing after extraction.

Top-level items inside each profile bundle:
- README.md / run_all.py / pyproject.toml
- configs/
- src/
- tests/
- docs/
- run_manifest.json
- environment_report.json (when available)
- logs/
- stage_00/ ... stage_07/

Each `stage_XX/` directory corresponds to a single profile (Standard or Extended), so there is no extra nested `results/stage_XX/<profile>/` layer inside these profile bundles.
